description:
[English]
=========================

Hello, everyone.
Since the last time, I made the animation “The adventure of ConstructorMeemral&Demoucjusz”, I looking forward to do the next animation, and the time when I studying Japanese, I found out an animation call “Gag Manga Biyori (ギャグマンガ日和)” , some of it really give me inspiration, that’s why I decide to make this animation, the characters using the same as ConstructorMeemral, and this time add in Soldier Colgate and Lyra heavy, so this animation was born, as one brand new episode of the series of “ Meemral&Demoucjusz ”
This animation audio is Chinese version, and the subtitle is Chinese too, after upload it, I will add on the English subtitle, hope this super hyper funny , with the spirit of Gmod and delightful animation light up your everyday. Thank you
Your support is my best reward, hope I will make more animation next time.

See you next time.

Sean.M


[中文]
=========================

大家好，親王又來也
自從上次上傳動畫「建築師Meemral大冒險」，我一直在尋找全新的動畫靈感來源，而在學習日語的期間，無意的接觸到了「搞笑日和漫畫(ギャグマンガ日和)」，裡面特殊的笑點給了我很大的啟發，而使我決定以這動畫作為Meemral系列的續集
除了原本的建築師Meemral和DJDemoucjusz再度爆笑聯袂登場，還新增了Soldier Colgate與LyraHeavy，並且使用中文音檔，其實不得不承認，日和的大陸配音真的非常有喜感，有把原本的笑點精華表現出來
願這爆笑、繼承Gmod精神的動畫消你煩惱，並也期望持續的啟發使我繼續製作動畫，而您們的支持與回饋就是我更新的動力，感謝您
我們下次見


親王
